in Energy w/o fuel (dmnl)} + Energy.Renewable_Energy_Output_Share_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Renewable Energy Output Share (dmnl)} + Energy.share_of_GDP_invested_in_Energy_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{share of GDP invested
in Energy (dmnl)}</eqn>
