1 to 20 Years (Mp/year)} + Population.deaths_20_to_40_years_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Deaths
20 to 40 Years (Mp/year)} + Population.deaths_40_to_60_years_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Deaths
40 to 60 Years (Mp/year)} + Population.deaths_60_to_80_years_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Deaths
60 to 80 Years (Mp/year)} + Population.deaths_Over_80_years_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Deaths Over 80 Years (Mp/year)} + Population.population_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Population (Mp} + Population.fertility_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Fertility (dmnl)} + Population.Births_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Births (Mp/year} + Population.total_deaths_by_PCTILE[PCTILE]{Total Death (Mp/year}</eqn>
